metadata.name: PaddleAway
metadata.description:
PaddleAway

The Ocean, where I am one, where calm consumes you and where the best thoughts are had. 

You can choose to be at one with the ocean and all the beauty and changes she brings, you can embrace her and adapt, or you can swim away.

I choose to be at one and stay.
